# StringExtras

```dart
extension StringExtras on String
```

Source: lib/src/extensions.dart:20:31

An extension on [String] that adds utility methods.

## Methods

### exclaim() → String

Source: lib/src/extensions.dart:22:22

Returns this string with an exclamation mark appended.

```dart
String exclaim() => '$this!';
```

---
### firstSegment() → String

Source: lib/src/extensions.dart:30:30

Splits this string by `/` and returns the first segment.

```dart
final path = 'usr/local/bin';
print(path.firstSegment()); // prints "usr"
```

```dart
String firstSegment() => split('/').first;
```

